{"tid":23981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東鐵線沿線鐵路係唔係唔再發展？","createTime":"2016-12-05T09:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T16:46:56.000Z","uid":24400,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f18d1dd842ce35730858dfe05b17398f1b5cfcab","tid":23981,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"東鐵線上水至沙田交通都一般般<br />\n住得入少少坐車去地鐵站都要半個鐘左右<br />\n例如北區醫院、粉嶺聯和墟、汀角、大埔中心、禾輋...以上地方附近都住唔少人<br />\n<br />\n計埋等車仲耐<br />\n有地方得一條路仲會塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但鐵路咁多年都冇發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪唔再發展？"},{"pid":"ba22e9aa9f67d19997b228e5b9f6637bda79add1","tid":23981,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a084804dfa99aab37a7f7d9dd48825d720e9a115","tid":23981,"uid":35229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"禾輋行去火炭都唔洗十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d89ef6409c380f58a11c096cb18f97f83fce53f","tid":23981,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:23:05.000Z","msg":"落馬洲支線<br />\n古洞北"},{"pid":"e08548ab7917d7dca1269cdeb3378f8435828a07","tid":23981,"uid":50182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:26:11.000Z","msg":"住粉嶺慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae9242237715f09d4f3d196f5df18aa9b0b47a5","tid":23981,"uid":14738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:28:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住粉嶺慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上水屎都冇得你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm